  • 已过时的接口 
    接口和说明
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnDetectUrlFileListener
    this callback can not detect the url file which bigger than 2G, use OnDetectBigUrlFileListener instead
  • 已过时的类 
    类和说明
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager
    use FileDownloader instead
  • 已过时的异常错误 
    异常错误和说明
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnDeleteDownloadFileListener.OnDeleteDownloadFileFailReason
    use OnDeleteDownloadFileListener.DeleteDownloadFileFailReason instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnDetectUrlFileListener.DetectUrlFileFailReason
    use OnDetectBigUrlFileListener and OnDetectBigUrlFileListener.onDetectUrlFileFailed(String, DetectBigUrlFileFailReason) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnFileDownloadStatusListener.OnFileDownloadStatusFailReason
    use OnFileDownloadStatusListener.FileDownloadStatusFailReason instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnMoveDownloadFileListener.OnMoveDownloadFileFailReason
    use OnMoveDownloadFileListener.MoveDownloadFileFailReason instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnRenameDownloadFileListener.OnRenameDownloadFileFailReason
    use OnRenameDownloadFileListener.RenameDownloadFileFailReason instead
  • 已过时的字段 
    字段和说明
    org.wlf.filedownloader.listener.OnFileDownloadStatusListener.FileDownloadStatusFailReason.TYPE_FILE_IS_DOWNLOADING
    not an error,not use since 0.2.0
  • 已过时的方法 
    方法和说明
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.createAndStart(String, String, String, OnFileDownloadStatusListener)
    use FileDownloadManager.createAndStart(String, String, String) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloader.detect(String, OnDetectUrlFileListener)
    this method can not detect the url file which bigger than 2G, use FileDownloader.detect(String, OnDetectBigUrlFileListener)instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.detect(String, OnDetectUrlFileListener)
    this method can not detect the url file which bigger than 2G, use FileDownloadManager.detect(String, OnDetectBigUrlFileListener)instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.file_download.DownloadTaskManager.detect(String, OnDetectUrlFileListener, DownloadConfiguration)
    this method can not detect the url file which bigger than 2G, use DownloadTaskManager.detect(String, OnDetectBigUrlFileListener, DownloadConfiguration)instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.DownloadFileInfo.getDownloadedSize()
    use DownloadFileInfo.getDownloadedSizeLong() instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.getDownloadFileBySavePath(String, boolean)
    use FileDownloadManager.getDownloadFileBySavePath(String) and FileDownloadManager.getDownloadFileByTempPath(String) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.getDownloadFileByUrl(String)
    use FileDownloadManager.getDownloadFile(String) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.base.BaseUrlFileInfo.getFileSize()
    use BaseUrlFileInfo.getFileSizeLong() instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.reStart(List, OnFileDownloadStatusListener)
    use FileDownloadManager.reStart(List) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.reStart(String, OnFileDownloadStatusListener)
    use FileDownloadManager.reStart(String) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.start(List, OnFileDownloadStatusListener)
    use FileDownloadManager.start(List) instead
    org.wlf.filedownloader.FileDownloadManager.start(String, OnFileDownloadStatusListener)
    use FileDownloadManager.start(String) instead
